DESCRIPTION

    This is version 3.01 of a cheat program for "Alien Breed 3D" by
    Team 17. It supports:
      - Floppy AB3D as distributed by Team 17
      - Patched AB3D with 8-channel stero sound added, available from
        the Team 17 ftp site ftp2.team17.com and Aminet.
      - AB3D CD32 version

    Also compatible with HackAB3D.

    Provides:
    - infinite energy
    - infinite ammunition for all weapons (once collected).
    - joypad/joystick compatibility patch

    Does not modify your game executable on disk.

    From v2.00, does not require you to decrunch your Alien Breed 3D
    executable.


